query: SELECT a.id, a.accountName, a.accountPlan, a.accountStatus, s.id as sub_id, s.subPlanId, s.subStatus, p.planName, p.planKey FROM accounts a LEFT JOIN subscriptions s ON s.subAccountId = a.id LEFT JOIN plans p ON p.id = s.subPlanId;
